t of content, set this to a lower number to avoid timeouts.'=>'Eyi n gba awọn ọrọ Aifọwọyi ti a ṣeto rẹ laaye lati ṣiṣẹ ni awọn ẹgbẹ. Ti o ba ni akoonu pupọ, ṣeto eyi si nọmba kekere lati yago fun awọn idaduro akoko.','Batches wait time'=>'Akoko idaduro awọn ẹgbẹ','This is the wait time (in seconds) between processing batches of Auto Terms. If you have a lot of existing content, set this to a higher number to avoid timeouts.'=>'Eyi ni akoko idaduro (ni awọn aaya) laarin processing awọn ẹgbẹ ti Awọn ọrọ Aifọwọyi. Ti o ba ni akoonu pupọ ti o wa tẹlẹ, ṣeto eyi si nọmba ti o ga julọ lati yago fun awọn idaduro akoko.','24 hours ago'=>'Wakati 24 sẹyin','7 days ago'=>'Ọjọ 7 sẹyin','2 weeks ago'=>'ọsẹ 2 sẹyin','1 month ago'=>'osù 1 sẹyin','6 months ago'=>'oṣu mẹfa sẹyin','1 year ago'=>'ọdún 1 sẹyin','Limit Auto Terms, based on published date'=>'Limiti Awọn Ọrọ Aifọwọyi, da lori ọjọ ti a tẹjade','This setting can limit your scheduled Auto Terms query to only recent content. We recommend using this feature to avoid timeouts on large sites.'=>'Iṣeto yii le ṣe idiwọ ibeere Awọn Ọrọ Aifọwọyi rẹ ti a ṣe eto si akoonu tuntun nikan. A ṣe iṣeduro lilo ẹya yii lati yago fun awọn akoko idaduro lori awọn aaye nla.','Save Settings'=>'Fipamọ Awọn Eto','Test Run'=>'Tẹtesti Iṣiṣẹ','Recent Schedule Runs'=>'Awọn Iṣiṣẹ Ẹrọ Tuntun','You can see full log details on the %1s screen'=>'O le rii alaye log pipe lori iboju %1s','Auto Terms Logs'=>'Awọn Log Awọn Ọrọ Aifọwọyi','Terms Display'=>'Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ','Terms Display successfully deleted.'=>'Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ ti a paarẹ ni aṣeyọri.','Post Type'=>'post type','Cloud'=>'Awọsanma','WordPress Default'=>'WordPress Default','Table List'=>'Atokọ Tabeli','Border Cloud'=>'Awọsanma Aala','Parent / Child'=>'Ẹbi / Ọmọ','Add New Terms Display'=>'Fi Awọn Ifihan Ọrọ Tuntun Kun','This feature allows you to create a customizable display of all the terms in one taxonomy.'=>'Ẹya yii ngbanilaaye fun ọ lati ṣẹda ifihan ti a le ṣe adani ti gbogbo awọn ọrọ ninu taxonomy kan.','Search Terms Display'=>'Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ Wiwa','Manage Terms Display'=>'Ṣakoso Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ','Preview Terms Display'=>'Ṣayẹwo Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ','Move up'=>'Gbe soke','Move down'=>'Gbe sẹhin','Edit Terms Display'=>'Ṣatunkọ Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ','Add new Terms Display'=>'Fi Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ Tuntun kun','To create more Terms Display, please upgrade to TaxoPress Pro.'=>'Lati ṣẹda diẹ ẹ sii Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ, jọwọ pọ si TaxoPress Pro.','With TaxoPress Pro, you can create unlimited Terms Display. You can create Terms Display for any taxonomy and then display those Terms Display anywhere on your site.'=>'Pẹlu TaxoPress Pro, o le ṣẹda Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ ailopin. O le ṣẹda Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ fun eyikeyi taxonomy ati lẹhinna fi Ifihan Awọn Ọrọ wọle nibikibi lori aaye rẹ.','Choose Terms'=>'Yan Awọn Ọrọ','Exceptions'=>'Awọn Ikuna','Display Format'=>'Fọọmu Ifihan','Hide title in output?'=>'Ṣe jẹ ki akọle wa ni abajade?','All post types'=>'Gbogbo awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ','All Parent Terms'=>'Gbogbo Awọn Ọrọ Obi','Parent Term'=>'Ọrọ Obi','Display only Parent Terms'=>'Fi Awọn Ọrọ Obi nikan han','Display only Sub-Terms'=>'Fi Awọn Ọrọ-ọrun nikan han','Display Parents and Sub-Terms'=>'Fi Awọn Obi ati Awọn Ọrọ-ọrun han','Display Mode'=>'Ìmúdàgba Àwòrán','Term selection mode'=>'Ìmúdàgba yiyan ọ̀rọ̀','Automatic'=>'Àkọ́kọ́','Display terms based on settings in the "General" tab.'=>'Ṣàfihàn àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ gẹ́gẹ́ bí àtọka tó wà nínú taabu "Gbogbogbo".','Custom'=>'Àwọn ìṣàkóso','Display only the specific terms entered in the "Custom terms to display" field below.'=>'Ṣàfihàn àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ pàtó tó wà nínú àgbègbè "Àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ ìṣàkóso láti ṣàfihàn" ní isalẹ.','Combined'=>'Apapọ̀','Display automatic terms plus any additional custom terms specified below.'=>'Ṣàfihàn àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ àkọ́kọ́ pẹ̀lú àwọn ìṣàkóso míì tó wà ní isalẹ.','Custom terms to display'=>'Àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ ìṣàkóso láti ṣàfihàn','Enter terms (comma-separated) to display. Used in Custom and Combined modes.'=>'Tẹ̀síwájú àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ (pẹlu àmì kóma) láti ṣàfihàn. A lo nínú Àwọn ìṣàkóso àti Apapọ̀.','Limit terms based on timeframe'=>'Dín àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ kù gẹ́gẹ́ bí àkókò','Ascending'=>'Ọ̀nà gígùn','Descending'=>'Ọ̀nà kìkà','Ordering for choosing terms for display'=>'Ìtòsọ́tọ̀ fún yiyan àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ láti ṣàfihàn','Text to display before terms list'=>'Ọ̀rọ̀ láti ṣàfihàn kí àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ tó wà nínú àtòka','Enter the text that should be display before terms list. This field accepts basic HTML.'=>'Tẹ̀síwájú ọ̀rọ̀ tó yẹ kí ó ṣàfihàn kí àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ tó wà nínú àtòka. Àgbègbè yìí gba HTML ipilẹ.','Text to display after terms list'=>'Ọ̀rọ̀ láti ṣàfihàn lẹ́yìn àtòka àwọn ọ̀rọ̀','Enter the text that should be display after terms list. This field accepts basic HTML.'=>'Tẹ̀síwájú ọ̀rọ̀ tó yẹ kí ó ṣàfihàn lẹ́yìn àtòka àwọn ọ̀rọ̀. Àgbègbè yìí gba HTML ipilẹ.','Exclude terms from terms display'=>'Yọ àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ kúrò nínú àfihàn àwọn ọ̀rọ̀','Enter terms (comma-separated) to exclude from the terms display.'=>'Tẹ̀síwájú àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ (pẹlu àmì kóma) láti yọ kúrò nínú àfihàn àwọn ọ̀rọ̀.','Exclude hidden terms from Terms Display?'=>'Ṣe o fẹ lati yọ awọn ọrọ ti a pa mọ kuro ninu ifihan Awọn ọrọ?','Hide display output if no terms?'=>'Ṣe o fẹ lati pa ifihan jade ti ko ba si awọn ọrọ?','Maximum terms to display'=>'Iye to pọ julo ti awọn ọrọ lati fi han','This is the color of the least popular term'=>'Eyi ni awọ ti ọrọ ti ko gbajumọ julọ','This is the color of the most popular term'=>'Eyi ni awọ ti ọrọ ti o gbajumọ julọ','Term display div class'=>'Iru ifihan ọrọ div kilasi','This option allows you to change the format of your terms. You can use any of the tokens in the "Terms Display format" sidebar". Find more details %1sin the documentation%2s.'=>'Yiyan yii jẹ ki o yipada ọna kika ti awọn ọrọ rẹ. O le lo eyikeyi ninu awọn ami ni " ọna kika ifihan Awọn ọrọ" sidebar". Wa alaye diẹ sii %1sni iwe-itumọ%2s.','You\'re using TaxoPress Free.
                                        The Pro version has more features and support.'=>'O nlo TaxoPress Free. 
                                        Ẹya Pro ni awọn ẹya diẹ sii ati atilẹyin.','Font size minimum must not be greater than Font size maximum value.'=>'Iwọn fonti ti o kere ju ko gbọdọ tobi ju iye iwọn fonti ti o pọ julo lọ.','Save Terms Display'=>'Fipamọ Ifihan Awọn ọrọ','Add Terms Display'=>'Fikun awọn Ifihan Awọn ọrọ','Terms Display format'=>'Ọna kika Ifihan Awọn ọrọ','Here are the tokens you can use for Term link format'=>'Eyi ni awọn ami ti o le lo fun ọna kika ọna asopọ ọrọ','The URL of the term'=>'URL ti ọrọ naa','The ID of the term'=>'ID ti ọrọ naa','The weighted size of the term in the display'=>'Iwọn ti a ṣe akiyesi ti ọrọ naa ninu ifihan','The number of times the term is used'=>'Iye igba ti ọrọ naa ti lo','This provides rel tag markup'=>'Eyi n pese akọle tag rel','it creates'=>'o n ṣẹda','The font size for the term'=>'Iwọn fonti fun ọrọ naa','The font color for the term'=>'Ẹ̀dá àwọ̀ fún ìsọ̀rọ̀','The name of the term'=>'Orúkọ ìsọ̀rọ̀','The name of the term with any HTML stripped out'=>'Orúkọ ìsọ̀rọ̀ pẹ̀lú HTML kankan tí a yọkúrò','The description of the term'=>'Àpejuwe ìsọ̀rọ̀','Invalid nonce'=>'Nonce tí kò tọ́','Missing display ID.'=>'ID àfihàn tí a padà sílẹ̀.','Invalid terms display configuration.'=>'Ìṣètò àfihàn ìsọ̀rọ̀ tí kò tọ́.','There are no terms in this taxonomy.'=>'Kò sí ìsọ̀rọ̀ nínú taxonomy yìí.','Please provide a taxonomy to delete'=>'Jọ̀wọ́ pèsè taxonomy kan láti pa','Please provide a taxonomy name'=>'Jọ̀wọ́ pèsè orúkọ taxonomy kan','Object'=>'Ohun kan','%s has been successfully added'=>'%s ti ṣàfikún pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí','%s has failed to be added'=>'%s ti kuna láti ṣàfikún','%s has been successfully updated'=>'%s ti ṣe àtúnṣe pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí','%s has failed to be updated'=>'%s ti kuna láti ṣe àtúnṣe','%s has been successfully deleted'=>'%s ti pa pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí','%s has failed to be deleted'=>'%s ti kuna láti pa','Nonce failed verification'=>'Nonce ti kuna ìmúlò','Please choose a different taxonomy name. %s is already registered.'=>'Jọ̀wọ́ yan orúkọ taxonomy míràn. %s ti forúkọsílẹ̀ tẹlẹ.','Please provide a post type to attach to.'=>'Jọ̀wọ́ pèsè post type kan láti so pọ̀ mọ́.','Please choose a different post type name. %s matches an existing page slug, which can cause conflicts.'=>'Jọwọ yan orukọ post type miiran. %s ba a slug oju-iwe to wa tẹlẹ mu, eyi le fa awọn ariyanjiyan.','Please do not use quotes in post type/taxonomy names or rewrite slugs'=>'Jọwọ ma ṣe lo awọn ẹtọ ninu awọn orukọ post type/taxonomy tabi tun kọ awọn slug','%s has been successfully imported'=>'%s ti gbe wọle ni aṣeyọri','%s has failed to be imported'=>'%s ti kuna lati gbe wọle','Add new %s'=>'Fi %s tuntun kun','Edit %s'=>'Ṣatunkọ %s','New %s'=>'Tuntun %s','View %s'=>'Wo %s','All %s'=>'Gbogbo %s','Search %s'=>'Wa %s','No %s found.'=>'Ko si %s ti a ri.','No %s found in trash.'=>'Ko si %s ti a ri ninu ikọsẹ.','Popular %s'=>'Olokiki %s','Parent %s'=>'Ibi %s','Parent %s:'=>'Ibi %s:','Update %s'=>'Ṣatunkọ %s','New %s name'=>'Orukọ %s tuntun','Separate %s with commas'=>'Ya %s lọtọ pẹlu awọn koma','Add or remove %s'=>'Fi %s kun tabi yọkuro','Choose from the most used %s'=>'Yan lati inu %s ti a lo julọ','Kindly select an action in bulk action dropdown!'=>'Jọwọ yan iṣe kan ninu akojọ aṣayan iṣe bulọọki!','Kindly select atleast one taxonomy to proceed'=>'Jọwọ yan o kere ju taxonomy kan lati tẹsiwaju','Taxonomy has been successfully deactivated'=>'Taxonomy ti wa ni aṣeyọri ti wa ni pa','Taxonomy has been successfully activated'=>'Taxonomy ti wa ni aṣeyọri ti wa ni mu ṣiṣẹ','Taxonomy has been successfully deleted'=>'Taxonomy ti wa ni aṣeyọri ti wa ni paarẹ','Are you sure you want to delete this? Deleting will NOT remove created content.'=>'Ṣe o da ọ loju pe o fẹ pa eyi? Piparẹ kii yoo yọ akoonu ti a ṣẹda kuro.','Please select at least one post type.'=>'Jọwọ yan o kere ju ọkan ninu awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ.','Taxonomy slug cannot be numbers only.'=>'Taxonomy slug ko le jẹ awọn nọmba nikan.','Taxonomies'=>'Taxonomies','Add New'=>'Fi Tuntun Kun','This feature allows you to create new taxonomies and edit all the settings for each taxonomy.'=>'Iwọn yi n jẹ ki o ṣẹda awọn taxonomy titun ati satunkọ gbogbo awọn eto fun ọkọọkan taxonomy.','Search Taxonomies'=>'Wa Taxonomies','All Taxonomies'=>'Gbogbo Taxonomies','Public Taxonomies'=>'Taxonomies Gbogbo eniyan','Private Taxonomies'=>'Taxonomies Ikọkọ','All Post Types'=>'Gbogbo Awọn iru Ifiweranṣẹ','Invalid nonce. Request is not authorized.'=>'Nonce ti ko wulo. Ibeere ko ni aṣẹ.','Manage Taxonomy'=>'Ṣakoso Taxonomy','Edit Taxonomy'=>'Ṣatunkọ Taxonomy','Add new Taxonomy'=>'Fi Taxonomy tuntun kun','Permalinks'=>'Permalinks','Admin Area'=>'Admin Area','Other Labels'=>'Other Labels','REST API'=>'REST API','Order'=>'Order','Slug'=>'Slug','Deactivate or Delete'=>'Deactivate or Delete','Taxonomy Slug'=>'Taxonomy Slug','Slug has changed'=>'Slug ti yipada','Slug already exists'=>'Slug ti wa tẹlẹ','Special character not allowed in slug.'=>'A ko gba ohun kikọ pataki laaye ninu slug.','The “slug” is the URL-friendly version of the name. It is usually all lowercase and contains only letters, numbers, and underscores.'=>'“slug” ni ẹya ti o dara fun URL ti orukọ. O maa n jẹ gbogbo lẹta kekere ati pe o ni awọn lẹta, awọn nọmba, ati awọn underscore nikan.','DO NOT EDIT the taxonomy slug unless also planning to migrate terms. Changing the slug registers a new taxonomy entry.'=>'MA ṢE ṢATUNKỌ slug taxonomy ayafi ti o ba gbero lati gbe awọn ọrọ naa. Yiyipada slug n gba iforukọsilẹ titun ti taxonomy.','Migrate terms to newly renamed taxonomy?'=>'Ṣe gbe awọn ọrọ si taxonomy ti a tun pe ni tuntun?','(e.g. Jobs)'=>'(e.g. Jobs)','Plural Label'=>'Plural Label','(e.g. Job)'=>'(e.g. Job)','Singular Label'=>'Singular Label','Parent-Child Relationships'=>'Ibasepo Ọmọ-Ẹbi','Can terms in this taxonomy be organized into hierarchical relationships?'=>'Ṣe awọn ọrọ ninu taxonomy yii le ṣe eto sinu ibasepọ hierarchical?','Description'=>'Apejuwe','Describe what your taxonomy is used for.'=>'Ṣalaye ohun ti taxonomy rẹ nlo fun.','Default Terms'=>'Àwọn Ọrọ Àkọ́kọ́','Set the default terms for this taxonomy. These will be automatically added to all new posts. Enter the term names or slugs. Separate multiple terms with by comma.'=>'Ṣeto awọn ọrọ àkọ́kọ́ fun taxonomy yii. Awọn wọnyi yoo jẹ aifọwọyi fi kun gbogbo awọn ifiweranṣẹ tuntun. Tẹ awọn orukọ ọrọ tabi awọn slugs. Ya awọn ọrọ pupọ pẹlu koma.','Archive page result'=>'Abajade oju-iwe akọọlẹ','Normally, WordPress will only show one post type on taxonomy archive pages. Enable this feature to show content from all selected posts types.'=>'Ni deede, WordPress yoo fihan iru ifiweranṣẹ kan ṣoṣo lori awọn oju-iwe akọọlẹ taxonomy. Mu ẹya yii ṣiṣẹ lati fihan akoonu lati gbogbo awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a yan.','Rewrite'=>'Tun kọ','WordPress can use a custom permalink for this taxonomy. It does not have to match the slug.'=>'WordPress le lo permalink aṣa fun taxonomy yii. Ko gbọdọ ba slug mu.','(default: taxonomy name)'=>'(aifọwọyi: orukọ taxonomy)','Custom Rewrite Slug'=>'Aṣa Tun Kọ Slug','Custom taxonomy rewrite slug.'=>'Slug tun kọ taxonomy aṣa.','Rewrite With Front'=>'Tun Kọ Pẹlu Iwaju','Should the permastruct be prepended with the front base.'=>'Ṣe permastruct yẹ ki o wa ni a fi kun pẹlu ipilẹ iwaju.','Rewrite Hierarchical'=>'Tun Kọ Hierarchical','Should the permastruct allow hierarchical urls.'=>'Ṣe permastruct gba awọn URL hierarchical laaye.','Show user interface'=>'Fihan oju-iwe olumulo','Should there be a visible interface in the WordPress admin area to manage these terms?'=>'Ṣe yẹ ki o wa oju-iwe ti o han ni agbegbe iṣakoso WordPress lati ṣakoso awọn ọrọ wọnyi?','Show in admin menus'=>'Fihan ninu awọn akojọ aṣayan alakoso','Should there be links to this taxonomy in the WordPress admin menus?'=>'Ṣe yẹ ki o wa awọn ọna asopọ si taxonomy yii ninu awọn akojọ aṣayan alakoso WordPress?','Show in frontend menus'=>'Fihan ninu awọn akojọ aṣayan iwaju','Should this taxonomy be available for the frontend “Menus” and “Navigation” options?'=>'Ṣe taxonomyi yi yẹ ki o wa fun awọn aṣayan “Menus” ati “Navigation” ni iwaju?','Show admin column'=>'Fi iha admin han','Should a column for this taxonomy appear on screens such as “Posts” and “Pages”?'=>'Ṣe iha fun taxonomyi yi yẹ ki o han lori awọn iboju bii “Posts” ati “Pages”?','Show in "Quick Edit" and "Bulk Edit"'=>'Fi han ni "Quick Edit" ati "Bulk Edit"','Should this taxonomy be available in editing tools on screens such as “Posts” and “Pages”?'=>'Ṣe taxonomyi yi yẹ ki o wa ninu awọn irinṣẹ ṣiṣatunkọ lori awọn iboju bii “Posts” ati “Pages”?','Show in Filter'=>'Fi han ninu Àlẹmọ','Should this taxonomy be available in filters on screens such as “Posts” and “Pages”?'=>'Ṣe taxonomyi yi yẹ ki o wa ninu awọn àlẹmọ lori awọn iboju bii “Posts” ati “Pages”?','Menu Name'=>'Orukọ Menu','Custom admin menu name for your taxonomy.'=>'Orukọ menu admin aṣa fun taxonomyi rẹ.','(e.g. All Jobs)'=>'(e.g. Gbogbo Awọn Iṣẹ)','All Items'=>'Gbogbo Awọn nkan','Used as tab text when showing all terms for hierarchical taxonomy while editing post.'=>'Lo bi ọrọ taabu nigbati o ba n ṣafihan gbogbo awọn ọrọ fun taxonomy hierarchical nigba ṣiṣatunkọ ifiweranṣẹ.','(e.g. Edit Job)'=>'(e.g. Ṣatunkọ Iṣẹ)','Edit Item'=>'Ṣatunkọ Nkan','Used at the top of the term editor screen for an existing taxonomy term.'=>'Lo ni oke iboju olootu ọrọ fun ọrọ taxonomy to wa tẹlẹ.','(e.g. View Job)'=>'(e.g. Wo Iṣẹ)','View Item'=>'Wo Nkan','Used in the admin bar when viewing editor screen for an existing taxonomy term.'=>'Lo ninu bar admin nigbati o ba n wo iboju olootu fun ọrọ taxonomy to wa tẹlẹ.','(e.g. Update Job Name)'=>'(e.g. Imudojuiwọn Orukọ Iṣẹ)','Update Item Name'=>'Imudojuiwọn Orukọ Nkan','Custom taxonomy label. Used in the admin menu for displaying taxonomies.'=>'Aami taxonomy aṣa. Ti lo ninu akojọ admin fun ifihan taxonomies.','Update %s name'=>'Imudojuiwọn %s orukọ','(e.g. Add New Job)'=>'(e.g. Fi Iṣẹ Tuntun Kún)','Add New Item'=>'Fi Ohun Tuntun Kún','Used at the top of the term editor screen and button text for a new taxonomy term.'=>'Ti lo ni oke iboju olootu ọrọ ati ọrọ bọtini fun ọrọ taxonomy tuntun.','(e.g. New Job Name)'=>'(e.g. Orukọ Iṣẹ Tuntun)','New Item Name'=>'Orukọ Ohun Tuntun','(e.g. Parent Job)'=>'(e.g. Iṣẹ Abáni)','Parent Item'=>'Ohun Abáni','(e.g. Parent Job:)'=>'(e.g. Iṣẹ Abáni:)','Parent Item Colon'=>'Kolonu Ohun Abáni','(e.g. Search Jobs)'=>'(e.g. Wa Awọn Iṣẹ)','Search Items'=>'Wa Awọn Ohun','(e.g. Popular Jobs)'=>'(e.g. Awọn Iṣẹ Olokiki)','Popular Items'=>'Awọn Ohun Olokiki','(e.g. Separate Jobs with commas)'=>'(e.g. Ya Awọn Iṣẹ pẹlu awọn koma)','Separate Items with Commas'=>'Ya Awọn Ohun pẹlu Awọn Koma','(e.g. Add or remove Jobs)'=>'(e.g. Fi tabi yọ Awọn Iṣẹ)','Add or Remove Items'=>'Fi tabi Yọ Awọn Ohun','(e.g. Choose from the most used Jobs)'=>'(e.g. Yan lati ọdọ Awọn Iṣẹ ti a lo julọ)','Choose From Most Used'=>'Yan Lati Ọpọ Ti A Lo Jùlọ','(e.g. No jobs)'=>'(àpẹẹrẹ: Ko si iṣẹ)','No terms'=>'Ko si awọn ọrọ','Used when indicating that there are no terms in the given taxonomy associated with an object.'=>'Lo nigbati o ba tọka si pe ko si awọn ọrọ ninu taxonomy ti a fun ni ti o ni nkan kan.','No %s'=>'Ko si %s','(e.g. Jobs list navigation)'=>'(àpẹẹrẹ: Iṣakojọpọ iṣẹ)','Items List Navigation'=>'Iṣakojọpọ Awọn ohun','Screen reader text for the pagination heading on the term listing screen.'=>'Ọrọ kika iboju fun akọle pagination lori iboju atokọ ọrọ.','%s list navigation'=>'%s iṣakojọpọ','(e.g. Jobs list)'=>'(àpẹẹrẹ: Atokọ iṣẹ)','Items List'=>'Atokọ Awọn ohun','Screen reader text for the items list heading on the term listing screen.'=>'Ọrọ kika iboju fun akọle atokọ awọn ohun lori iboju atokọ ọrọ.','%s list'=>'%s atokọ','(e.g. No jobs found)'=>'(àpẹẹrẹ: Ko si iṣẹ ti a rii)','Not Found'=>'Ko ri','The text displayed via clicking ‘Choose from the most used items’ in the taxonomy meta box when no items are available.'=>'Ọrọ ti a fihan nipasẹ titẹ ‘Yan lati awọn ohun ti a lo jùlọ’ ninu apoti meta taxonomy nigbati ko si awọn ohun ti o wa.','No %s found'=>'Ko si %s ti a rii','(e.g. &larr; Back to jobs'=>'(àpẹẹrẹ: &larr; Pada si awọn iṣẹ','Back to Items'=>'Pada si Awọn ohun','The text displayed after a term has been updated for a link back to main index.'=>'Ọrọ ti a fihan lẹyin ti a ti ṣe imudojuiwọn ọrọ kan fun ọna asopọ pada si itọsọna akọkọ.','Back to %s'=>'Pada si %s','Show in REST API'=>'Fihan ni REST API','Add the taxonomy to the WordPress wp-json API.'=>'Fi taxonomy kun si WordPress wp-json API.','REST API base slug'=>'REST API ipilẹ slug','The base slug that this taxonomy will use in the REST API.'=>'Slug ipilẹ ti taxonomy yii yoo lo ninu REST API.','REST API controller class'=>'REST API olukọni kilasi','The name of a custom Rest Controller class instead of WP_REST_Terms_Controller.'=>'Orukọ ti kilasi Olukọni Rest aṣa dipo WP_REST_Terms_Controller.','Custom controller to use instead of WP_REST_Terms_Controller.'=>'Olukọni aṣa lati lo dipo WP_REST_Terms_Controller.','Public'=>'Public','The taxonomy is for public use. It can be seen by frontend users.'=>'Taxonomy yii jẹ fun lilo gbogbogbo. O le ri i nipasẹ awọn olumulo iboju iwaju.','Public Queryable'=>'Public Queryable','The taxonomy is publicly queryable.'=>'Taxonomy yii jẹ ti a le beere ni gbogbogbo.','Query Var'=>'Query Var','Enable a custom query_var key for this taxonomy.'=>'Mu bọtini query_var aṣa ṣiṣẹ fun taxonomy yii.','Custom Query Var String'=>'Akọsile Query Var Aṣa','Sets a custom query_var slug for this taxonomy.'=>'Ṣeto slug query_var aṣa fun taxonomy yii.','Metabox callback'=>'Metabox ipe','Sets a callback function name for the meta box display. Hierarchical default: post_categories_meta_box, non-hierarchical default: post_tags_meta_box. To remove the metabox completely, use "false".'=>'Ṣeto orukọ iṣẹ ipe fun ifihan apoti meta. Aiyipada hierarchical: post_categories_meta_box, aiyipada ti kii ṣe hierarchical: post_tags_meta_box. Lati yọ metabox naa patapata, lo "false".','Categories'=>'Categories','This feature controls the order of %s when you\'re editing posts, and in frontend displays.'=>'Iṣẹ yii n ṣakoso aṣẹ ti %s nigbati o ba n ṣatunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ, ati ni awọn ifihan iboju iwaju.','Enable TaxoPress ordering'=>'Mu aṣẹ TaxoPress ṣiṣẹ','Enable TaxoPress ordering for this taxonomy in the frontend and admin area.'=>'Mu aṣẹ TaxoPress ṣiṣẹ fun taxonomy yii ni iwaju ati agbegbe admin.','Re-activate Taxonomy'=>'Tun-ṣe aṣẹ Taxonomy','Deactivate Taxonomy'=>'Pa aṣẹ Taxonomy','Delete Taxonomy'=>'Pa Taxonomy','Delete TaxoPress Edit Data'=>'Pa Data Edit TaxoPress','You can only delete taxonomies created with TaxoPress. However, you can delete any changes or edit made from TaxoPress which will remove TaxoPress version edit restoring original taxonomies data or removing it if already deleted'=>'O le pa awọn taxonomy nikan ti a ṣẹda pẹlu TaxoPress. Sibẹsibẹ, o le pa eyikeyi awọn ayipada tabi awọn atunṣe ti a ṣe lati TaxoPress ti o yoo yọ awọn ayipada ẹya TaxoPress ti o mu data taxonomy atilẹba pada tabi yọ o ti o ba ti pa a tẹlẹ','Save Taxonomy'=>'Fipamọ Taxonomy','Add Taxonomy'=>'Fi Taxonomy kun','Term copied successfully.'=>'Ọrọ ti a daakọ ni aṣeyọri.','Term deleted successfully.'=>'Ọrọ ti a pa ni aṣeyọri.','Term removed from all posts successfully.'=>'Ọrọ ti a yọ lati gbogbo awọn ifiweranṣẹ ni aṣeyọri.','Count'=>'Iye','Custom URL'=>'URL aṣa','Synonyms'=>'Awọn ọrọ itumọ','Linked Terms'=>'Awọn ọrọ ti o so pọ','Status'=>'Ipo','Copy'=>'Daakọ','Select Destination Taxonomy'=>'Yan Taxonomy Ibi-afẹde','Search posts'=>'Wa awọn ifiweranṣẹ','post type'=>'post type','Select Destination %s'=>'Yan Ibi %s','Filter'=>'Fọ́ọ́tù','Terms deleted successfully.'=>'Àwọn ìtàn ti parẹ́ ní aṣeyọrí.','Term(s) copied successfully.'=>'Ìtàn(à) ti daakọ́ ní aṣeyọrí.','Hidden'=>'Títọ́','Live'=>'Míì','No terms found.'=>'Kò sí ìtàn tí a rí.','Quick edit &#8220;%s&#8221; inline'=>'Àtúnṣe kíákíá &#8220;%s&#8221; inú','Quick&nbsp;Edit'=>'Àtúnṣe&nbsp;Kíákíá','Remove From All Posts'=>'Yọ Kúrò Nínú Gbogbo Àwọn Ìtàn','View'=>'Wo','Quick Edit'=>'Àtúnṣe Kíákíá','Cancel'=>'Fagile','Update'=>'Ṣàtúnṣe','Terms'=>'Àwọn ìtàn','This screen allows you to search and edit all the terms on your site.'=>'Ibè yi n jẹ́ kí o wa àti ṣe àtúnṣe gbogbo àwọn ìtàn lórí aaye rẹ.','This screen allows you to order terms via drag and drop.'=>'Ibè yi n jẹ́ kí o paṣẹ àwọn ìtàn nípasẹ̀ fifi wọn soke àti ṣiṣan wọn.','Search Terms'=>'Wa Àwọn Ìtàn','Media Tags'=>'Àwọn Tágì Media','Media Tag'=>'Àkọsílẹ Media','All Media Tags'=>'Gbogbo Àkọsílẹ Media','Edit Media Tag'=>'Ṣatunkọ Àkọsílẹ Media','View Media Tag'=>'Wo Àkọsílẹ Media','Update Media Tag name'=>'Ṣatunkọ orukọ Àkọsílẹ Media','Add new Media Tag'=>'Fi Àkọsílẹ Media tuntun kun','New Media Tag name'=>'Orukọ Àkọsílẹ Media tuntun','Parent Media Tag'=>'Àkọsílẹ Media Obi','Parent Media Tag:'=>'Àkọsílẹ Media Obi:','Search Media Tags'=>'Wa Àkọsílẹ Media','Popular Media Tags'=>'Àkọsílẹ Media olokiki','Separate Media Tags with commas'=>'Ya Àkọsílẹ Media pẹlu awọn koma','Add or remove Media Tags'=>'Fi tabi yọ Àkọsílẹ Media','Choose from the most used Media Tags'=>'Yan lati inu Àkọsílẹ Media ti a lo julọ','No Media Tags found'=>'Ko si Àkọsílẹ Media ti a ri','No Media Tags'=>'Ko si Àkọsílẹ Media','Media Tags list navigation'=>'Iṣakoso atokọ Àkọsílẹ Media','Media Tags list'=>'Atokọ Àkọsílẹ Media','Back to Media Tags'=>'Pada si Àkọsílẹ Media','TaxoPress Logs'=>'TaxoPress Logs','Search TaxoPress Logs'=>'Wa Awọn igbasilẹ TaxoPress','Edit TaxoPress Logs'=>'Ṣatunkọ Awọn igbasilẹ TaxoPress','Update TaxoPress Logs'=>'Ṣe imudojuiwọn Awọn igbasilẹ TaxoPress','Add New TaxoPress Logs'=>'Fi Awọn igbasilẹ TaxoPress Tuntun Kun','New TaxoPress Logs'=>'Awọn igbasilẹ TaxoPress Tuntun','You\'re using TaxoPress Free. The Pro version has more features and support. %sUpgrade to Pro%s'=>'O nlo TaxoPress Free. Ẹya Pro ni awọn ẹya diẹ sii ati atilẹyin. %sGbe si Pro%s','Upgrade to TaxoPress Pro'=>'Gbe si TaxoPress Pro','Enhance the power of TaxoPress with the Pro version:'=>'Mu agbara TaxoPress pọ pẹlu ẹya Pro:','Unlimited “Term Display”'=>'“Ifihan Ọrọ” ti ko ni ihamọ','Unlimited “Terms for Current Posts”'=>'“Awọn Ọrọ fun Awọn ifiweranṣẹ Tẹlẹ” ti ko ni ihamọ','Unlimited “Related Posts”'=>'“Awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti o ni ibatan” ti ko ni ihamọ','Unlimited “Auto Links”'=>'“Awọn ọna asopọ aifọwọyi” ti ko ni ihamọ','Unlimited “Auto Terms”'=>'“Awọn Ọrọ aifọwọyi” ti ko ni ihamọ','Create new terms using OpenAI and other sources'=>'Ṣẹda awọn ọrọ tuntun nipa lilo OpenAI ati awọn orisun miiran','Use Linked Terms'=>'Lo Awọn Ọrọ ti a So','Use Synonyms'=>'Lo Awọn ọrọ ti o jọra','Schedule Auto Terms to run automatically'=>'Ṣeto Awọn Ọrọ aifọwọyi lati ṣiṣẹ laifọwọyi','Control the display of term metaboxes'=>'Ṣakoso ifihan ti awọn apoti metabox ọrọ','Fast, professional support'=>'Atilẹyin yarayara, ọjọgbọn','No ads inside the plugin'=>'Ko si awọn ipolowo ninu afikun naa','Need TaxoPress Support?'=>'Ṣe o nilo atilẹyin TaxoPress?','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'Ti o ba nilo iranlọwọ tabi ti o ni ibeere ẹya tuntun, jẹ ki a mọ.','Request Support'=>'Beere Atilẹyin','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'Iwe aṣẹ alaye ni a tun wa lori oju opo wẹẹbu afikun naa.','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ibi Ẹkọ','OpenAI Integration'=>'Isopọ OpenAI','TaxoPress Pro allows you to integrate OpenAI to analyze your content and suggest terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati dapọ OpenAI lati ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ.','IBM Watson Integration'=>'Isopọ IBM Watson','TaxoPress Pro allows you to integrate Watson to analyze your content and suggest terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati dapọ Watson lati ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ.','Dandelion Integration'=>'Isopọ Dandelion','TaxoPress Pro allows you to integrate Dandelion to analyze your content and suggest terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati dapọ Dandelion lati ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ.','LSEG / Refinitiv Integration'=>'Isopọ LSEG / Refinitiv','TaxoPress Pro allows you to integrate LSEG / Refinitiv to analyze your content and suggest terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati dapọ LSEG / Refinitiv lati ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ.','Suggest terms using AI'=>'Daba awọn ọrọ nipa lilo AI','TaxoPress Pro allows you to suggest new terms for your content using the OpenAI. This service can analyze your content and suggest new terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati daba awọn ọrọ tuntun fun akoonu rẹ nipa lilo OpenAI. Iṣẹ yii le ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ tuntun.','TaxoPress Pro allows you to suggest new terms for your content using the IBM Watson. This service can analyze your content and suggest new terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati daba awọn ọrọ tuntun fun akoonu rẹ nipa lilo IBM Watson. Iṣẹ yii le ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ tuntun.','Copy with Metadata'=>'Daakọ pẹlu Metadata','Auto terms using AI'=>'Awọn ọrọ aifọwọyi nipa lilo AI','TaxoPress Pro allows you to generate new terms for your content using the OpenAI, IBM Watson, Dandelion and Open Calais services. These services can analyze your content and add new terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati ṣẹda awọn ọrọ tuntun fun akoonu rẹ nipa lilo OpenAI, IBM Watson, Dandelion ati awọn iṣẹ Open Calais. Awọn iṣẹ wọnyi le ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si fi awọn ọrọ tuntun kun.','TaxoPress Pro allows you to suggest new terms for your content using the OpenAI, IBM Watson, Dandelion and Open Calais services. These services can analyze your content and suggest new terms.'=>'TaxoPress Pro gba ọ laaye lati daba awọn ọrọ tuntun fun akoonu rẹ nipa lilo OpenAI, IBM Watson, Dandelion ati awọn iṣẹ Open Calais. Awọn iṣẹ wọnyi le ṣe itupalẹ akoonu rẹ ki o si daba awọn ọrọ tuntun.','Add Custom Elements'=>'Fi Awọn eroja adani kun','TaxoPress Pro allows you complete control over where Auto Links are added. You can choose to skip any HTML elements that appear in your content.'=>'TaxoPress Pro n jẹ ki o ni iṣakoso pipe lori ibi ti a ti fi Auto Links kun. O le yan lati fo gbogbo awọn eroja HTML ti o han ninu akoonu rẹ.','Use Regular Expressions to modify Auto Terms'=>'Lo Awọn ilana deede lati ṣe atunṣe Awọn ọrọ Auto','TaxoPress Pro allows you to change how Auto Terms analyzes your posts. You will need to know how to write Regular Expressions to use this feature.'=>'TaxoPress Pro n jẹ ki o yi bi Awọn ọrọ Auto ṣe n ṣe itupalẹ awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ pada. Iwọ yoo nilo lati mọ bi a ṣe le kọ Awọn ilana deede lati lo ẹya yii.','This feature allows you to connect terms. When the main term or any of these terms are added to the post, all the other terms will be added also.'=>'Eyi jẹ ẹya kan ti o fun laaye lati so awọn ọrọ pọ. Nigbati ọrọ pataki tabi eyikeyi ninu awọn ọrọ wọnyi ba wa ni afikun si ifiweranṣẹ, gbogbo awọn ọrọ miiran yoo tun wa ni afikun.','Linked Terms Feature'=>'Ẹya Awọn ọrọ ti o so pọ','TaxoPress Pro allows you to create powerful connections between your terms. When one term is added to a post, its linked terms can be automatically added too. This helps maintain consistent organization across your content.'=>'TaxoPress Pro n jẹ ki o ṣẹda awọn asopọ ọlọrọ laarin awọn ọrọ rẹ. Nigbati ọrọ kan ba wa ni afikun si ifiweranṣẹ, awọn ọrọ ti o so mọ rẹ le tun wa ni afikun laifọwọyi. Eyi ṣe iranlọwọ lati pa iṣeto ti o ni iduroṣinṣin kọja akoonu rẹ.','This feature allows you to associate additional words with each term. For example, "website" can have synonyms such as "websites", "web site", and "web pages".'=>'Eyi jẹ ẹya kan ti o fun laaye lati so awọn ọrọ afikun pọ pẹlu ọkọọkan ọrọ. Fun apẹẹrẹ, "website" le ni awọn itumọ gẹgẹbi "websites", "web site", ati "web pages".','Synonyms Terms Feature'=>'Ẹya Awọn itumọ','TaxoPress Pro allows you to have multiple words associated with a single term. If TaxoPress scans your content and finds a synonym, it will act as if it has found the main term.'=>'TaxoPress Pro n jẹ ki o ni awọn ọrọ pupọ ti a so mọ ọrọ kan. Ti TaxoPress ba wo akoonu rẹ ki o si rii itumọ kan, yoo ṣiṣẹ bi ẹnipe o ti ri ọrọ pataki.','Taxonomy Display'=>'Ihan taxonomy','This feature is available in TaxoPress Pro'=>'Eyi jẹ ẹya ti o wa ni TaxoPress Pro','Customize the display of terms in the TaxoPress metabox.'=>'Ṣe adani ihamọ awọn ọrọ ninu metabox TaxoPress.','Options include checkboxes and a dropdown list.'=>'Awọn aṣayan pẹlu awọn apoti ayẹwo ati atokọ isalẹ.','Copy Term with Metadata'=>'Daakọ Ọrọ pẹlu Metadata','To Copy terms with their metadata, please upgrade to pro.'=>'Lati daakọ awọn ọrọ pẹlu metadata wọn, jọwọ ṣe imudojuiwọn si pro.','With TaxoPress Pro, you can duplicate taxonomy terms along with all their metadata. This includes term descriptions, images, and custom fields. You can copy terms between taxonomies to maintain consistent organization across your site.'=>'Pẹlu TaxoPress Pro, o le ẹda awọn ọrọ taxonomy pẹlu gbogbo metadata wọn. Eyi pẹlu awọn apejuwe ọrọ, awọn aworan, ati awọn aaye adani. O le daakọ awọn ọrọ laarin awọn taxonomy lati pa iṣeto ti o ni iduroṣinṣin kọja aaye rẹ.','Choose the display formats of your terms, options include table list, ordered list, border-cloud and lots more.'=>'Yan awọn ọna kika ihamọ ti awọn ọrọ rẹ, awọn aṣayan pẹlu atokọ tabili, atokọ aṣẹ, awọ-oorun-ọṣọ ati ọpọlọpọ diẹ sii.','Hourly'=>'Ni wakati','Daily'=>'Ni ọjọ','Pro Feature'=>'Ẹya Pro','Some of these features are available in TaxoPress Pro'=>'Diẹ ninu awọn ẹya wọnyi wa ni TaxoPress Pro','ID'=>'ID','Name (Pro)'=>'Orukọ (Pro)','Counter (Pro)'=>'Iṣiro (Pro)','Random (Pro)'=>'Ayanfẹ (Pro)','Term Order (Pro)'=>'Ilana Ọrọ (Pro)','Method for choosing terms for display'=>'Ọna fun yiyan awọn ọrọ fun ifihan','Name'=>'Orukọ','Counter'=>'Iṣiro','Term Order'=>'Ilana Ọrọ','Disabled'=>'Dènà','You have disabled TaxoPress ordering'=>'O ti dènà ilana TaxoPress','Terms in this taxonomy are ordered by %s'=>'Awọn ọrọ ninu taxonomy yii ti wa ni ilana nipasẹ %s','Term Order(Pro)'=>'Ilana Ọrọ (Pro)','Upgrade to TaxoPress Pro to use Term Order to manually order Terms'=>'Ṣe imudojuiwọn si TaxoPress Pro lati lo Ilana Ọrọ lati ṣe ilana awọn Ọrọ ni ọwọ','Request completed.'=>'Ibéèrè ti pari.','Security error. Kindly reload this page and try again'=>'Aṣiṣe aabo. Jọwọ tun gba oju-iwe yii ki o gbiyanju lẹẹkansii','Permission error. You do not have permission to manage taxopress'=>'Aṣiṣe aṣẹ. O ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣakoso TaxoPress','Posts content and title is empty.'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ akoonu ati akọle jẹ ofo.','Permission error. You do not have permission to preview this post.'=>'Aṣiṣe igbanilaaye. O ko ni igbanilaaye lati wo ifiweranṣẹ yii.','You do not have permission to manage this taxonomy. Enable Metabox Access Taxonomies for this role in %1sTaxoPress Settings%2s.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣakoso taxonomy yii. Mu Metabox Access Taxonomies ṣiṣẹ fun ipa yii ni %1sTaxoPress Settings%2s.','Term Results'=>'Term Results','No results found for this post with this taxonomy.'=>'Ko si awọn abajade ti a rii fun ifiweranṣẹ yii pẹlu taxonomy yii.','Invalid Auto Term ID. Please save the settings before using preview.'=>'ID Auto Term ti ko tọ. Jọwọ fipamọ awọn eto ṣaaju ki o to lo iworan.','You must enable at least one AI integration source to use auto term preview.'=>'O gbọdọ mu orisun iṣọpọ AI kan ṣiṣẹ o kere ju lati lo iworan auto term.','This Auto Terms option is not enabled for metaboxes. Please enable it in the Auto Terms settings.'=>'Aṣayan Auto Terms yii ko ti mu ṣiṣẹ fun awọn metaboxes. Jọwọ mu ṣiṣẹ ni awọn eto Auto Terms.','Click %1s to select or deselect them from this %2s.'=>'Tẹ %1s lati yan tabi yọ wọn kuro ninu %2s yii.','Suggest Existing Terms'=>'Ṣe iṣeduro Awọn Ọrọ Tẹlẹ','OpenAI'=>'OpenAI','IBM Watson'=>'IBM Watson','Dandelion'=>'Dandelion','LSEG / Refinitiv'=>'LSEG / Refinitiv','Update %1s on this %2s'=>'Imudojuiwọn %1s lori %2s yii','Existing Terms not found for the selected post type and taxonomies'=>'Ko si Awọn Ọrọ Tẹlẹ ti a rii fun iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a yan ati taxonomies','Existing Terms taxonomy is required. Kindly select taxonomies and save the settings before running preview.'=>'Taxonomy Awọn Ọrọ Tẹlẹ jẹ dandan. Jọwọ yan taxonomies ki o si fipamọ awọn eto ṣaaju ki o to ṣe iworan.','Result from ajax request.'=>'Abajade lati ibeere ajax.','The selected taxonomy is not associated with the selected post type.'=>'Taxonomy ti a yan ko ni asopọ pẹlu iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a yan.','No results found for this taxonomy.'=>'Ko si awọn abajade ti a rii fun taxonomy yii.','You do not have permission to edit this post.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ yii.','Click Term to select or deselect from this %1s'=>'Tẹ Term lati yan tabi yọ kuro ninu %1s yi','Both Taxonomy and Post are required.'=>'Meji Taxonomy ati Post ni a nilo.','No new terms were selected or deselected.'=>'Ko si awọn ọrọ tuntun ti a yan tabi ti yọ kuro.','%1s terms added to this %2s.'=>'%1s ọrọ ti a fi kun si %2s yi.','%1s terms removed from this %2s.'=>'%1s ọrọ ti a yọ kuro ninu %2s yi.','You do not have capability to manage this taxonomy.'=>'Iwọ ko ni agbara lati ṣakoso taxonomy yi.','Terms cannot contain the following characters: %s'=>'Awọn ọrọ ko le ni awọn ohun kikọ wọnyi: %s','Terms must be at least %d characters long.'=>'Awọn ọrọ gbọdọ jẹ o kere ju %d awọn ohun kikọ lọ.','Terms cannot exceed %d characters.'=>'Awọn ọrọ ko le kọja %d awọn ohun kikọ.','The Dandelion integration is disabled in the Legacy AI Sources settings.'=>'Iṣopọ Dandelion jẹ ti a pa ni eto Legacy AI Sources.','No matched result from the API Server.'=>'Ko si abajade ti o baamu lati API Server.','The Dandelion integration requires an API Key. Please add your API Key in the Auto Term settings.'=>'Iṣopọ Dandelion nilo API Key. Jowo fi API Key rẹ kun ni eto Auto Term.','Selected content is empty.'=>'Akopọ ti a yan jẹ ofo.','Result from cache.'=>'Abajade lati cache.','API Error: %1s.'=>'API Aṣiṣe: %1s.','Result from api.'=>'Abajade lati api.','Error establishing connection with the API server. Try again.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni iṣeto asopọ pẹlu API server. Gbiyanju lẹẹkan si.','The LSEG / Refinitiv integration is disabled in the Legacy AI Sources settings.'=>'Iṣopọ LSEG / Refinitiv jẹ ti a pa ni eto Legacy AI Sources.','The LSEG / Refinitiv integration requires an API Key. Please add your API Key in the Auto Term settings.'=>'Iṣopọ LSEG / Refinitiv nilo API Key. Jowo fi API Key rẹ kun ni eto Auto Term.','API Error: No matched result for content.'=>'API Aṣiṣe: Ko si abajade ti o baamu fun akoonu.','The IBM Watson integration is disabled in the Legacy AI Sources settings.'=>'Iṣọpọ IBM Watson ti wa ni pa ni awọn eto Legacy AI Sources.','The IBM Watson integration requires an API Key and URL. Please add your API Key in the Auto Term settings.'=>'Iṣọpọ IBM Watson nilo bọtini API ati URL. Jọwọ fi bọtini API rẹ kun ni awọn eto Auto Term.','The OpenAI integration requires an API Key. Please add your API Key in the Auto Term settings.'=>'Iṣọpọ OpenAI nilo bọtini API. Jọwọ fi bọtini API rẹ kun ni awọn eto Auto Term.','Invalid placeholder(s) detected: {%s}. Valid placeholders are: {content}, {post_terms}, {site_terms}'=>'A ti ṣe awari aṣiṣe placeholder: {%s}. Awọn placeholders ti o wulo ni: {content}, {post_terms}, {site_terms}','You added {post_terms} in the prompt but your post does not contain any terms.'=>'O ti fi {post_terms} kun ni iwifunni ṣugbọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ ko ni eyikeyi awọn ọrọ.','You added {site_terms} in the prompt but your site does not contain any terms for this taxonomy.'=>'O ti fi {site_terms} kun ni iwifunni ṣugbọn aaye rẹ ko ni awọn ọrọ fun taxonomy yii.','Error: OpenAI says there is an issue with this API key. Please check your plan or billing details.'=>'Aṣiṣe: OpenAI sọ pe iṣoro wa pẹlu bọtini API yii. Jọwọ ṣayẹwo eto rẹ tabi awọn alaye isanwo.','Show All Existing Terms'=>'Fihan Gbogbo Awọn Ọrọ Tí Ó Wà','Manage Post Terms'=>'Ṣakoso Awọn Ọrọ Ifiweranṣẹ','Auto Terms'=>'Awọn Ọrọ Auto','Create Terms'=>'Ṣẹda Awọn Ọrọ','View Existing Terms'=>'Wo Awọn Ọrọ Tí Ó Wà','This feature allows you to browse all the terms in a taxonomy.'=>'Iṣẹ yii fun ọ laaye lati ṣawari gbogbo awọn ọrọ ni taxonomy.','View Current Post Terms'=>'Wo Awọn Ọrọ Ifiweranṣẹ lọwọlọwọ','This feature allows you to manage all the terms that are currently attached to a post.'=>'Iṣẹ yii fun ọ laaye lati ṣakoso gbogbo awọn ọrọ ti o wa lọwọlọwọ ti o ni asopọ si ifiweranṣẹ kan.','View Terms'=>'Wo Awọn Ọrọ','This feature allows you to browse based on selected auto terms settings and sources.'=>'Iṣẹ yii fun ọ laaye lati ṣawari da lori awọn eto awọn ọrọ auto ti a yan ati awọn orisun.','Suggest Terms'=>'Ṣe iṣeduro Awọn Ọrọ','Select all %1s'=>'Yan gbogbo %1s','Deselect all %1s'=>'Yọ gbogbo %1s','Select %1s'=>'Yan %1s','Please choose a post to use with TaxoPress AI.'=>'Jọwọ yan ifiweranṣẹ kan lati lo pẹlu TaxoPress AI.','Label can\'t be empty.'=>'Aami ko le jẹ ofo.','Label can\'t exceed 30 characters.'=>'Aami ko le kọja awọn ohun kikọ 30.','Unknown tab type.'=>'Iru taabu ti ko ni imọ.','Error saving label.'=>'Aṣiṣe fipamọ aami.','Please choose a post to preview.'=>'Jọwọ yan ifiweranṣẹ kan lati ṣe afihan.','Metaboxes'=>'Metaboxes','Metabox Settings'=>'Awọn eto Metabox','Metabox Access'=>'Iwọle Metabox','This feature allows you to customize the metabox interface you see when adding terms to posts.'=>'Ẹya yii ngbanilaaye fun ọ lati ṣe akanṣe oju-ibaraenisepo metabox ti o rii nigbati o ba n fi awọn ọrọ kun awọn ifiweranṣẹ.','Save Changes'=>'Fipamọ Iyipada','Select...'=>'Yan...','Select %s'=>'Yan %s','Invalid request.'=>'Ìbéèrè aṣiṣe.','No terms in your WordPress database.'=>'Ko si awọn ọrọ ninu ipilẹ data WordPress rẹ.','There\'s no content to scan.'=>'Ko si akoonu lati ṣawari.','No results from your WordPress database.'=>'Ko si awọn esi lati ipilẹ data WordPress rẹ.','There are no terms that are relevant to your content.'=>'Ko si awọn ọrọ ti o ni ibatan si akoonu rẹ.','Tags'=>'Awọn aami','This user does not have access to manage any of this post attached taxonomies. Enable Metabox Access Taxonomies for this role in %1sTaxoPress Settings%2s.'=>'Olumulo yii ko ni iraye si lati ṣakoso eyikeyi ninu awọn taxonomy ti a so mọ ifiweranṣẹ yii. Mu Metabox Access Taxonomies ṣiṣẹ fun ipa yii ni %1sTaxoPress Settings%2s.','No TaxoPress Metabox features are enabled for this post type.'=>'Ko si awọn ẹya Metabox TaxoPress ti a mu ṣiṣẹ fun iru ifiweranṣẹ yii.','Save, You can also press Enter to save and escape to cancel'=>'Fipamọ, O tun le tẹ Enter lati fipamọ ati Escape lati fagile','Search Terms...'=>'Ṣawari Awọn ọrọ...','Create Term'=>' ṣẹda Ọrọ','You do not have the required capabilities to manage any of this post attached taxonomies.'=>'Iwọ ko ni awọn agbara ti o nilo lati ṣakoso eyikeyi ninu awọn taxonomy ti a so mọ ifiweranṣẹ yii.','You can not edit this label.'=>'Iwọ ko le ṣatunkọ aami yii.','Invalid nonce token.'=>'Aami nonce ti ko tọ.','Label is too long.'=>'Aami naa ti gun ju.','Hey, you\'ve been using TaxoPress for %s on your site. We hope the plugin has been useful. Please could you quickly leave a 5-star rating on WordPress.org? It really does help to keep TaxoPress growing.'=>'Hey, o ti n lo TaxoPress fun %s lori aaye rẹ. A nireti pe afikun naa ti wulo. Jọwọ le ṣe ni kiakia fi diẹ ẹ sii ju 5-star ni WordPress.org? O ṣe iranlọwọ gaan lati jẹ ki TaxoPress n dagba.','1 week'=>'1 ọsẹ','3 months'=>'3 osu','Click here to add your rating for TaxoPress'=>'Tẹ nibi lati fi eyi rẹ fun TaxoPress','Maybe later'=>'Boya nigbamii','I already did'=>'Mo ti ṣe tẹlẹ','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'Eyi afikun le parẹ.','TaxoPress was not activated because TaxoPress Pro is already active. Please keep only TaxoPress Pro enabled.'=>'TaxoPress ko ti mu ṣiṣẹ nitori TaxoPress Pro ti wa ni aktivi tẹlẹ. Jọwọ pa nikan TaxoPress Pro mu ṣiṣẹ.','TaxoPress: Options'=>'TaxoPress: Awọn aṣayan','term nameName'=>'Orukọ','term nameTaxonomy'=>'Taxonomy']];